.env

# Local Hugging Face/Xet caches. They are reproducible download metadata, not
# experiment artifacts; in particular, a literal Windows-style cache path
# (for example `D:\\hf_cache`) is not checkoutable on Windows.
**/hf_cache/
**/xet/
**/D:*
**/outputs/
**/__pycache__/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/logs/*.log
**/logs/*.pid
**/logs/*.complete
